videos.headline: Matt Corral pass finds Dontario Drummond for Ole Miss TD
videos.description: Ole Miss takes a 10-0 lead over Texas A&M as Matt Corral completes a pass to Dontario Drummond for the 2-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Matt Corral pass finds Dontario Drummond for Ole Miss TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Isaiah Spiller gets hit behind the line for a safety
videos.description: Isaiah Spiller takes the handoff but can't get any breathing room as the Ole Miss defense swarms him for a safety.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Isaiah Spiller gets hit behind the line for a safety) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Devon Achane scoots his way to 24-yard TD for Texas A&M
videos.description: Texas A&M inches closer on the scoreboard thanks to Devon Achane slithering his way through defenders to score a 24-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Devon Achane scoots his way to 24-yard TD for Texas A&M) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zach Calzada throws pick-six in the 4th quarter
videos.description: Zach Calzada has his pass intercepted and returned 52 yards for a touchdown by AJ Finley to give Ole Miss a 29-13 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Zach Calzada throws pick-six in the 4th quarter) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Devon Achane runs for 9-yard Texas A&M TD
videos.description: Texas A&M cuts the score to 29-19 in the fourth quarter as Devon Achane runs 9-yards into the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Devon Achane runs for 9-yard Texas A&M TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Snoop Conner darts through the defense for 13-yard score
videos.description: Snoop Conner takes the handoff and navigates his way through traffic to score a 13-yard Ole Miss touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Snoop Conner darts through the defense for 13-yard score) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kiffin says Rebels' victory was a 'defensive win'
videos.description: In a game against No. 11 Texas A&M that was sealed by AJ Finley's pick-six, No. 15 Ole Miss' Lane Kiffin gives the credit to his defense.

videos.headline: Finley's pick-six seals Rebels' win in SEC thriller
videos.description: With time winding down in the fourth, No. 15 Ole Miss' AJ Finley brings home a game-sealing interception to beat No. 11 Texas A&M, 29-19. (edited)
